# SUBTRAJ.xyz (position file)
# SIZEX SIZEY SIZEZ (lattice parameter, a b c in Angstram)
# 0.5 (size of grid in Angstram)
# 2 (index of normal axis, 0: x, 1: y, 2: z)
# NUMFRAME (number of frames)
# 1 (resample every n frames, so-called 'ns' in code) 
